== Requirements

* RMagick (for creating CAPTCHA images)
http://rubyforge.org/projects/rmagick/

* crypt (for encrypt/decrypt CAPTCHA keys)
ruby -S gem install crypt --no-rdoc --no-ri

* EventMachine (for creating server)
ruby -S gem install eventmachine --no-rdoc --no-ri

* Revent (for RPC)
ruby -S gem install revent --no-rdoc --no-ri
